description:
Fallout 4's Next Gen Update on the ROG ALLY gaming system! In this video, we put the highly anticipated update to the test, showcasing real-time gameplay to see how the ASUSROG ALLY handles the enhanced graphics and improved mechanics of the game. Whether you're a seasoned gamer or new to the Fallout series this will give you an idea of how this handheld gaming pc performs. We test a few settings on the built in screen and we even test out Fallout 4 in docked modern the ROG Ally. Bonus, we also test one the best fallout games New Vegas
